4 HJR___ NAMING A PORTION OF HIGHWAY 21 IN THE TOWN OF MUNFORD
5 IN TALLADEGA COUNTY THE JACKIE SWINFORD MEMORIAL HIGHWAY.
6
7 WHEREAS, in honor of Jackie Swinford, this body
8 requests that the Department of Transportation designate the
9 portion of Highway 21 in the Town of Munford, Alabama, from
10 the South town limit to the North town limit the Jackie
11 Swinford Memorial Highway; now therefore,
12 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, BOTH
13 HOUSES THEREOF CONCURRING, That the Department of
14 Transportation is encouraged to coordinate with local
15 governing officials to consider naming the portion of
16 Highway 21 from the South town limit to the North town limit
17 the Jackie Swinford Memorial Parkway, and to erect several
18 appropriate signs or markers along the route, with
19 consideration to fiscal responsibility, consistent with
20 applicable requirements and laws, in recognition of this
21 designation.
